io.tarantool.driver.mappers

Interface MessagePackValueMapper

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Cloneable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultMessagePackMapper, TarantoolResultMapper

    public interface MessagePackValueMapper
extends Cloneable
    Basic interface for collection of generic converters between MessagePack entities and Java objects. Value converters must be added using the registerValueConverter(Class, Class, ValueConverter) method
